    "updated_at": "2016-03-01T11:54:38Z",
    "body": "Does the presence of this flag degrade gracefully? In other words, does this cause any problems for users on GTK2 systems? If it causes problems, we will have to implement this differently prevent _Breaking the Entire World_™.\n"
