    "created_at": "2016-03-01T12:20:23Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-01T12:20:23Z",
    "body": "We should not force every project that uses Electron to enforce their users to installing GTK3 just because they updated the version of Electron they built their app on...\n\nWhile we can make a change like this, keep in mind this is a breaking change unless the feature flag degrades gracefully. Unless someone can confirm the graceful degradation, I'm opposed to this change.\n\nThe alternative here is to make this flag opt-in.\n"
  },
