    "created_at": "2016-03-01T16:01:52Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-01T16:01:52Z",
    "body": "> [..] nobody these days has GTK2 installed but not GTK3\n\nIf that's the case across the general end-user base for Electron apps, then I'm :ok: with this.\n\n> We should do whatever Chrome 47 does\n\nBut that's the thing, GTK3 support is hardly stable yet. The Chromium folks are (or at least were last I checked) using deprecated GTK APIs and what not.\n\nWell, I guess worst case we can always revert this if all hell breaks loose, hehe :smiling_imp: \nLet's leave the final verdict up to @zcbenz.\n"
