    "updated_at": "2016-03-01T16:53:48Z",
    "body": "OK! i didn’t know that stability might be a problem, but generally chromium tests well and people already included [GTK3 theme integration](https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=132847), which might indicate sufficient stability.\n\ni researched a bit and it seems that the use of deprecated APIs [is intentional](https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src.git/+/c694003c15dc6af21b453febd1463c5394c98c9e).\n"
