    "created_at": "2016-03-05T08:10:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-05T08:10:00Z",
    "body": "The `use_gtk3` flag is only meaningful under Chromium's side, to enable GTK3 we need to enable it in libchromiumcontent first, and then change the link settings in Electron.\n\nChrome is not using GTK3 by default, unless your distribution manually enabled the flag for the package. For when will Chrome switch to use GTK3, you can track this issue: https://crbug.com/79722, it is quite close but not yet done.\n\nI'm closing this since it is actually not doing anything.\n"
